    <a title="Mike" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/165395-mike"><img alt="Mike" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1627500793p2/165395.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/51827528?book_show_action=true">Apr 07, 2009</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Mike" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Mike" href="/user/show/165395-mike">Mike</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780374130268" href="/book/show/2694468-the-counterlife">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer51827528" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer2499065152272581854">I don&apos;t know if this haunting novel stands up to the very best of Roth (<i>American Pastoral</i>, <i>Sabbath&apos;s Theater</i>, <i>Patrimony</i>, <i>The Ghost Writer</i>), but I know that it has colonized my brain, that I&apos;m going to have to keep returning to its wisdom and authority for a long time to come. </span>
  <span id="freeText2499065152272581854" style="display:none">I don't know if this haunting novel stands up to the very best of Roth (<i>American Pastoral</i>, <i>Sabbath's Theater</i>, <i>Patrimony</i>, <i>The Ghost Writer</i>), but I know that it has colonized my brain, that I'm going to have to keep returning to its wisdom and authority for a long time to come. </span>
  <a data-text-id="2499065152272581854" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
