<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/87434.Liberty"><img alt="Liberty: Incorporating Four Essays on Liberty" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1349086870l/87434._SX98_.jpg" />
